<li id="cite_note-horne-86"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-horne_86-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFHorne2000" class="citation book cs1">Horne, Dennis B. (2000). <span class="id-lock-limited" title="Free access subject to limited trial, subscription normally required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.google.com/books/edition/Bruce_R_McConkie/g971PAAACAAJ?hl=en"><i>Bruce R. McConkie: Highlights From His Life &amp; Teachings</i></a></span>. <a href="/wiki/Eborn_Books" title="Eborn Books">Eborn Books</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-890718-01-5" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-890718-01-5"><bdi>978-1-890718-01-5</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Bruce+R.+McConkie%3A+Highlights+From+His+Life+%26+Teachings&amp;rft.pub=Eborn+Books&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-890718-01-5&amp;rft.aulast=Horne&amp;rft.aufirst=Dennis+B.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FBruce_R_McConkie%2Fg971PAAACAAJ%3Fhl%3Den&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormon+views+on+evolution" class="Z3988"></span></span>
